{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_51_01",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 2.92
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "もしもし、お疲れ様です。……えっ！？　『ミラクル☆\nアイドルバースデー！』のお願い事、通ったんですか？",
      "startTime": 8.8333330989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "嬉しいに決まってます。クリスマスと誕生日が一緒\nだと、お祝いしてもらってばかりですから",
      "startTime": 16.3333330989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "今回は、私が内緒でみんなを喜ばせたいんです\nあ、サプライズですから、情報の取り扱いには――",
      "startTime": 24.6999990026,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4533.333059100002,
          "startTime": 29.2333320617
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃーん",
      "startTime": 30.4999977309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "わぁっ！？\nす、すみませんっ、それでは失礼します！",
      "startTime": 33.2999967137,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4590.000000000004,
          "startTime": 37.123330047
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、ごめんね。電話してたんだ",
      "startTime": 38.0999967137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "だ、大丈夫。もう切るとこだったから\n{user}さんと仕事の話をしてたの",
      "startTime": 46.2666633803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして\n『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』のこと？\nもうすぐお誕生日だもんね～。何をお願いするの？",
      "startTime": 53.9666666864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "え……あ……そ、そうね～。編集部の人達が\nなんでも実現してくれるらしいけど、ま、まだ迷ってて",
      "startTime": 64.5999964594,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "じー…………琴乃ちゃん、怪しい",
      "startTime": 70.3000015456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "なんでっ！？\nべ、べ、べ、別に普通だから！",
      "startTime": 77.0666682123,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3566.6666667000018,
          "startTime": 80.633334879
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "お、なんだか面白そうな話をしてますねぇ\nあの様子……なるほど～",
      "startTime": 86.4999990025,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4466.673004699998,
          "startTime": 90.9666720072
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃ～ん、聞きましたよ～。『ミラクル☆アイドル\nバースデー！』で、まさかあんなお願いをするなんて～",
      "startTime": 96.1661767044,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "えぇー！？　こころちゃん、知ってるの？\nずるい、教えてよ～",
      "startTime": 104.2333308099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "ま、待って、さっき決まったばっかりなのに\nこころが知ってる訳ないでしょ？　絶対嘘よ",
      "startTime": 111.4666600743,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ、知ってますよ～。まさかあんなに可愛い\nお願い事だなんて～。琴乃ちゃんらしいですけどね～",
      "startTime": 119.2999934076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "べ、別に可愛くないから！\nただ、みんなにプレゼントを配ろうと……。あ……",
      "startTime": 126.7333267409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 132.5833328444
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 132.5833328444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "いや～、琴乃ちゃん、ぽろっと言っちゃいましたね～\nこころの作戦通りです",
      "startTime": 137.9666661778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 140.2333328444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……隠しておきたかったのに……",
      "startTime": 140.2333328444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 145.6999944249
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、素敵なお願い事だよね。サプライズで\nプレゼントを渡すなんて、サンタさんみたいだし",
      "startTime": 149.6333277582,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 153.2333277582
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "二人のことも驚かせたかったのに……",
      "startTime": 153.2333277582,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 156.9999944249
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "まぁまぁ、こうして知ったのも何かの縁ですし\n二人で琴乃ちゃんに協力するのもいいかもですね～",
      "startTime": 160.8666610915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "全員分のプレゼントを選んだり\n買ってこないといけない訳ですから",
      "startTime": 166.8666600743,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "確かに大変そうだね……！\nねぇ、琴乃ちゃん、良ければ私達にも手伝わせて？",
      "startTime": 172.2666600743,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 177.3666560052
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、そう言われると、そうね……。分かった\n二人にはバレちゃったし、手伝ってもらうことにする",
      "startTime": 184.6666560052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 188.6999893385
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "わーい、よろしくお願いしま～す",
      "startTime": 188.6999893385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 195.6333226719
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん、やるからにはとことん盛り上げましょう\nもう、祭りだわっしょーーい！　みたいな感じで",
      "startTime": 195.6333226719,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 198.4333277582
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "がってんだ！！",
      "startTime": 198.4333277582,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 200.3666610915
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_01-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "ふ、二人とも……？\nそこまで派手なことはしないんだけど……",
      "startTime": 202.8666610915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
